1
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:28,439
Let me put it this way, boy.

2
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:32,760
Northern Tuluo Kingdom cavalry are fierce.

3
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:36,319
Every autumn, they raid our borders.

4
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,840
They abduct our people,

5
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,040
plunder our wealth and provisions,

6
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:41,959
and burn down civilian homes.

7
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:44,680
Though our forces hold the line,

8
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,280
we can only repel them temporarily.

9
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,519
But the grasslands are too vast.

10
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,159
When our troops pursue,

11
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:52,920
they often lose their bearings,

12
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:55,159
and frequently fall into ambushes.

13
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,200
Even if they cut their losses in time,

14
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:59,319
the front lines stretch too far.

15
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,879
Provisions and water supplies

16
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:02,920
cannot be guaranteed.

17
00:02:03,159 --> 00:02:06,200
So tell me, regarding this near-success,

18
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:08,360
how should it be handled?

19
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,000
This old fox is no simpleton.

20
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,840
He knows court affairs,

21
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,520
and understands border warfare.

22
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,759
I'd better test his depth.

23
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,400
You little brat.

24
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,840
Let me tell you something.

25
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:23,240
Writing poetry and the battlefield

26
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,960
are two completely different things.

27
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,240
On the battlefield,

28
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,280
there's no such thing as innate talent.

29
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:30,080
Even a martial arts master

30
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,360
on the battlefield

31
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,800
might still face the risk

32
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:35,360
of being killed by some nobody.

33
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,319
So, you little brat,

34
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,319
from now on,

35
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,039
don't go shooting your mouth off.

36
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:42,879
That's not fair.

37
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,639
My Young Master is still so young.

38
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:45,840
He hasn't studied military strategy,

39
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,960
nor has he been on a battlefield.

40
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,479
If he can't come up with a solution,

41
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,080
that's only natural.

42
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:53,360
If this brat went to battle,

43
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:56,439
he'd just wet his pants, I reckon.

44
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:59,159
Looking down on me, are you, old fox?

45
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:01,280
I'm afraid I'd scare you if I told you.

46
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,759
Oh, I'm so scared.

47
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,199
Come on, let's hear it.

48
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,759
It's simple.

49
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:09,039
Don't they just want people and supplies?

50
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:11,240
Have our soldiers disguise as civilians,

51
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,159
let them be captured,

52
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,319
then strike when they least expect it.

53
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:16,599
Catch them completely off guard.

54
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,080
Easier said than done.

55
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,360
How exactly would you strike?

56
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:24,479
Perhaps...

57
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,400
poison their provisions.

58
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:29,759
Ridiculous nonsense.

59
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:31,680
You little brat.

60
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:33,280
Do you think Tuluo Kingdom's generals

61
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,560
are just useless fools?

62
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,639
Seems this old man has some real skill.

63
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:38,479
A true sage hides among the common folk.

64
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:41,080
I was just joking earlier.

65
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,400
Now hear my real thoughts.

66
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,599
The grasslands are too vast.

67
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:48,680
We are unfamiliar with the terrain,

68
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,919
so we're indeed at a disadvantage.

69
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,120
Therefore,

70
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:52,680
rather than defending passively,

71
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,599
we should take the initiative.

72
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:58,960
Select hundreds of elites from our army,

73
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:00,840
infiltrate Tuluo Kingdom in disguise,

74
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,840
create chaos,

75
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,560
incite the people,

76
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,159
seize the mountains as warlords,

77
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,919
and rise against their court.

78
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:08,759
This is called

79
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,759
"breeding bandits to disturb a nation."

80
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,719
Then send envoys to neighboring states.

81
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,360
Have envoys from the neighboring states

82
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,120
arrange marriage alliances,

83
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:26,560
open trade routes, build connections,

84
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,279
to hold the Tuluo Kingdom in check.

85
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,079
If none of these methods work,

86
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,639
then we'll have to play dirty.

87
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,120
Take corpses of plague victims

88
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,600
along with some animal carcasses,

89
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:36,040
and dump them in Tuluo Kingdom's water

90
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,519
to spread plague within their borders.

91
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:41,639
Mass troops at the border, ready to strike

92
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,879
forcing Tuluo Kingdom on high alert.

93
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:47,439
A massed army consumes immense supplies.

94
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,600
With plague raging within,

95
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,279
and enemies lurking outside,

96
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,759
trouble from within and without,

97
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,399
Tuluo Kingdom can't take the pressure.

98
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,920
They'll surrender on their own.

99
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,160
Under such urgency,

100
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,399
this is all I could come up with.

101
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,839
Give me a bit more time,

102
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,120
or send me to the front lines,

103
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,720
and I can think of more strategies.

104
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,519
Are you sure

105
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,399
you've never studied the art of war?

106
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:16,560
I swear.

107
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,319
Young Master has barely read a few books.

108
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,279
Could it be that this kid

109
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,720
truly has extraordinary talent?

110
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,519
Damn right, I am extraordinarily gifted.

111
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:28,759
So what?

112
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:32,959
Don't try any stalling tactics with me.

113
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:33,879
Answer me this.

114
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,560
What's your relationship with Ning Ziming?

115
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:38,800
Your servant, Ning Ziming,

116
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,040
pays respects to Your Majesty.

117
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,639
Your humble servant...

118
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,560
Silence!

119
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,439
What is troubling Your Majesty?

120
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,360
Are you punishing me?

121
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,040
Could it be that recently

122
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,279
I have done something wrong?

123
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,120
My Minister Ning,

124
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,480
rise.

125
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

126
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,160
My Minister Ning.

127
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,360
Are you all right?

128
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,639
I am fine, Your Majesty.

129
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,000
My Minister Ning,

130
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,560
I have heard

131
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,600
that My Minister's eldest son, Ning Gan,

132
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,839
took part in this year's imperial exam.

133
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:07,879
Could it be

134
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,959
that my bribery for Ning Gan's exam

135
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,759
has reached His Majesty's ears?

136
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,319
In reply to Your Majesty,

137
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,480
yes, indeed.

138
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:19,240
Ning Gan has come of age,

139
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,560
having studied for many years.

140
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:23,120
It is time he served the nation

141
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:25,279
and shared the court's burdens.

142
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:27,920
Good. Very good.

143
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,480
You raised him well, My Minister Ning.

144
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:35,279
Have you read the poem I sent you?

145
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,680
Of what Your Majesty bestowed,

146
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,079
your humble servant has surely read it.

147
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:41,839
And what did you think?

148
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,480
Magnificent, sweeping thousands of miles.

149
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,399
Whoever composed such a poem

150
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,000
must possess extraordinary talent,

151
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:51,480
well-versed in our dynasty and Nanxuan.

152
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,519
Then in your view, My Minister Ning,

153
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:56,000
how does this man compare to Ning Gan?

154
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,120
Which is the better of the two?

155
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:00,399
Ning Gan cannot hold a candle to him.

156
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,439
And what of your other sons, My Minister?

157
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,120
Reporting to Your Majesty,

158
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:08,360
my second son Ning Xing, third Ning Mao

159
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,519
are mediocre in literary talent.

160
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,319
They dare not be compared to him.

161
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,959
You scheming Ning Ziming.

162
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,199
Still trying to deceive me.

163
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,120
And what

164
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,319
of your fourth son?

165
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,959
Why does His Majesty ask about Ning Chen?

166
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:30,040
Did someone expose me abandoning my family?

167
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,720
His Majesty most despises

168
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,759
heartless and faithless men.

169
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,080
Your humble servant confesses his guilt.

170
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:38,960
Your humble servant confesses his guilt.

171
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,720
I beg Your Majesty for mercy.

172
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,720
I beg Your Majesty for mercy!

173
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,399
Enough.

174
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,559
I summoned you here alone

175
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,120
not intending to punish you.

176
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:49,879
I simply feel

177
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,279
that the boy Ning Chen

178
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,720
is a fine young man.

179
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,279
You ought to show him more care.

180
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:55,360
As for me,

181
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:57,279
I can grant you one more chance.

182
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:58,679
But you must remember:

183
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,440
should you disappoint me again,

184
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,519
you shall ascend the Dragon Platform

185
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:05,639
and test if my royal blade is still sharp.

186
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,159
Your humble servant understands.

187
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,440
Your humble servant understands.

188
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:10,799
Your Majesty may rest assured.

189
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,960
When did His Majesty meet Ning Chen?

190
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,000
One more thing.

191
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,879
Ning Chen does not know my identity.

192
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:19,840
Therefore,

193
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,120
Of our talk as sovereign and minister,

194
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:24,159
I do not want anyone else to know.

195
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:24,960
This will not do.

196
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:26,919
I must hurry and find Ning Chen.

197
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:27,960
You may withdraw.

198
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,879
Your humble servant thanks Your Majesty.

199
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,240
Shipeng.

200
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,639
Summon the Crown Prince.

201
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,559
At once, Your Majesty.

202
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,360
Thank you for your trouble, Xiaomei.

203
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,080
Living quite comfortably, aren't you?

204
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,480
Wine and meat on the table.

205
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:57,519
When you left the manor,

206
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,240
did we not search you thoroughly?

207
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,240
Did you sneak out with manor valuables?

208
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,080
Bullshit.

209
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,360
I earned the money for this food myself.

210
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:07,080
It has nothing to do with Ning Manor.

211
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:08,919
What are you three doing here?

212
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,360
You're full of it.

213
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,200
We are Young Masters of the Ning Manor.

214
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,840
Do we need to report to you where we go?

215
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,279
This is Xiaomei's home.

216
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,559
You're not welcome here.

217
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:18,200
So you know it's someone else's home.

218
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,679
Then who are you to decide?

219
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,360
Exactly.

220
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:21,679
Ask this lowly maid yourself

221
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:23,399
if she dares to drive us away.

222
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:28,000
If the three Young Masters wish to come,

223
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,519
this servant naturally dares not object.

224
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:32,080
I only hope you can speak civilly.

225
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,799
Speak civilly, my ass.

226
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,039
Back at the Ning Manor,

227
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,720
this Bastard nearly killed me.

228
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:39,399
Now he wants to walk away and end it?

229
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,600
In your dreams.

230
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:42,159
What do you want?

231
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,200
To send you to see your mother, of course.

232
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,000
Get him!

233
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:45,879
Stop!

234
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,320
Big Brother.

235
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:04,919
I thought it was some martial arts master.

236
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,519
Turns out it's just an old cripple.

237
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:09,320
Do you know who I am?

238
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,799
Not just you three milk-mouthed brats,

239
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:16,240
even if your father Ning Ziming were here,

240
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,279
he wouldn't dare mock me.

241
00:11:18,639 --> 00:11:20,759
You old geezer, quite the nerve you have.

242
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:22,399
Calling my father by his name.

243
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:24,120
Watch I don't kill you for it.

244
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,919
Why waste words on them?

245
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:28,320
Today, even if the King of Heaven came,

246
00:11:28,519 --> 00:11:29,639
it wouldn't help.

247
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,960
Such big talk.

248
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:33,080
If you've got the guts, come try me.

249
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:34,639
You old fool.

250
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:35,919
Getting more worked up by the minute.

251
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,639
I... I...

252
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:39,519
Calm down.

253
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:43,600
He looks somewhat familiar to me.

254
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,080
Big Brother.

255
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:48,039
Anyone with that Bastard Ning Chen,

256
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,039
how important could they be?

257
00:11:49,519 --> 00:11:52,279
Probably just this maid's neighbor.

258
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,799
Right, Second Brother is correct.

259
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,720
If a few words could scare us off,

260
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:56,720
word would spread,

261
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:58,080
and we three brothers would become

262
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,559
the laughingstock of other Young Masters.

263
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:00,120
Exactly.

264
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:01,159
Mother gave us instructions anyway.

265
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,159
You stand back.

266
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:03,440
Leave this to me and Second Brother.

267
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,639
Right, right, come on.

268
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,200
You came here for me.

269
00:12:06,799 --> 00:12:07,679
Whatever it is, come at me.

270
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,080
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

271
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,519
Death is staring you in the face,

272
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:13,120
and you're still playing the hero.

273
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:16,120
Forgotten the wound on your neck already?

274
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:17,000
You...

275
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:21,519
I just let my guard down, that's all.

276
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:23,120
You damn dog.

277
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:23,919
Get him!

278
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,440
Look out!

279
00:12:40,279 --> 00:12:40,720
Xiaomei!

280
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:42,360
Young Master!

281
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:58,600
Young Master!

282
00:12:59,000 --> 00:12:59,480
Young Master!

283
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,200
